OOC: A funny thing about not really being involved in anything, really easy 
to come back.

::Aerotaur::
       After what seemed like weeks in search of his mysterious fruit 
Aerotaur gave up the search.  This wasn't much of a loss since he had no use 
for fruit anyway.  He finally managed to wander up to the bridge and looked 
around briefly.  "Hello?"

--part1_1b8.ce6cbb2.2b620fa4_boundary
